PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of the Environment, on behalf of the Government of Canada, to ENTER INTO A SUPPLEMENTARY AGREEMENT with the Government of Quebec to amend the Canada-Quebec Agreement on the St. Lawrence River 2011-2026, entered into on January 9, 2012, to update its seven appendices. The revised appendices would be valid for the period from April 1, 2021 to March 31, 2026.
